I need to identify the line items and value of costs incurred to secure customer orders and deliver goods and services to customers.

Looking at the income statement, the costs related to securing customer orders and delivering goods/services typically include:

1. Cost of Goods Sold - This represents the direct costs of producing goods sold
2. Selling Expenses - These are costs associated with marketing, sales, and delivering products

In the example, the "Selling Expenses" of 493854.67 was identified as the relevant cost.

Looking at the problem to solve, I can see that the "Selling Expenses" is 1334099.97, which represents the costs incurred to secure customer orders and deliver goods/services.
